Awak fikir awak boleh perangkap saya di sini

00:16:23.980 --> 00:16:25.100
seperti yang anda suka

00:16:25.540 --> 00:16:26.780
kerana awak Canselor?

00:16:35.540 --> 00:16:37.180
Anda tahu dengan baik

00:16:38.540 --> 00:16:39.740
sama ada saya mampu melakukan ini.

00:16:48.900 --> 00:16:49.740
Yu,

00:16:51.740 --> 00:16:52.580
awak takut.

00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:55.300
Setiap kali anda takut,

00:16:55.860 --> 00:16:56.860
anda mengepal penumbuk anda.

00:16:58.500 --> 00:16:59.380
Apabila anda gembira,

00:17:00.100 --> 00:17:01.100
awak suka menyanyi

00:17:01.500 --> 00:17:02.620
lagu tanpa lagu.

00:17:03.500 --> 00:17:04.640
Saya tahu awak cuba jadi kuat.

